            {
              "data": {},
              "content": [
                {
                  "data": {},
                  "marks": [],
                  "value": "It also flagged a problem with headings in my blog cards — they weren’t ordered sequentially. That’s a developer slip-up, and exactly the kind of issue Lighthouse makes easy to spot.",
